                            <comment id="14075895" author="rohini" created="Mon, 28 Jul 2014 05:49:13 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Ran test-tez. Hangs at TestStore, but if that is commented out everything passes. If TestStore is ran alone it passes. Can be reproduced by running test-tez with few tests before TestStore removing other tests. Gets stuck with &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;junit&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; 2014-07-27 21:09:48,856 &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;Timer-17&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; INFO  org.apache.pig.backend.hadoop.executionengine.tez.TezJob  - DAG Status: status=RUNNING, progress=TotalTasks: 1 Succeeded: 0 Running: 1 Failed: 0 Killed: 0, diagnostics=, counters=null&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;But there is no TezChild java process running and only DAGAppMaster process is running. Most likely a tez issue. While it got stuck in testSuccessFileCreation2 once, it got stuck in testCleanupOnFailureMultiStore next time. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Updated patch with 15 mins timeout for test-tez to get around that for now. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14076917" author="daijy" created="Mon, 28 Jul 2014 22:30:43 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Does TestStore hang before this patch?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14077014" author="rohini" created="Mon, 28 Jul 2014 23:22:21 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;yes. Have seen it timeout in the CI run before&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14077107" author="daijy" created="Tue, 29 Jul 2014 00:13:45 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;+1. Let&apos;s open a separate Jira to track TestStore occationally hang.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14077191" author="rohini" created="Tue, 29 Jul 2014 01:30:43 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Removed the skipping of tests in TestEvalPipeline2 as &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/TEZ-1257&quot; title=&quot;Error on empty partition when using OnFileUnorderedKVOutput and ShuffledMergedInput&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;TEZ-1257&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;TEZ-1257&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; is ready for check-in. Will run it once after it is available in maven repo and check in this patch.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14077226" author="daijy" created="Tue, 29 Jul 2014 01:54:12 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;+1, we can check in once &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/TEZ-1257&quot; title=&quot;Error on empty partition when using OnFileUnorderedKVOutput and ShuffledMergedInput&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;TEZ-1257&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;TEZ-1257&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; checked in.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14077390" author="rohini" created="Tue, 29 Jul 2014 06:00:23 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Also set TezConfiguration.TEZ_USE_CLUSTER_HADOOP_LIBS to true&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14077391" author="rohini" created="Tue, 29 Jul 2014 06:00:56 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Committed to trunk (0.14). Thanks for the review Daniel.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
